{"id": 1845, "genre": 1001, "title": "你在哪些方面可以称得上是“观察力爆表”？", "description": "那些自己都佩服自己的时刻！快来告诉我们你有多棒！", "record_count": 3865, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201708171052047ueEpVL8HZ3IPkaW.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-08-17T03:00:07Z", "options": [{"id": 229888, "content": "小时候看的动画片柯南中华一番小当家等开头没看到结局也没看到，全靠观察细节然后推测", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950981}, {"id": 232449, "content": "这个第一次见面的人能不能对它好", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 746748}, {"id": 229890, "content": "自动观察分析周围人的样貌体征和行为方式，后来出门就把眼镜摘掉", "image": null, "praise_count": 62, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950981}, {"id": 230146, "content": "看见吃的瞬间变百米飞人", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107688}, {"id": 231938, "content": "绿茶婊鉴定完毕！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1116470}, {"id": 229891, "content": "真的，朋友圈的妹子们谁失了恋进了生理期，我全知道", "image": null, "praise_count": 42, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950981}, {"id": 230147, "content": "观察别人的心情变化", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107690}, {"id": 237827, "content": "对方是否有狐臭", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1131466}, {"id": 229892, "content": "对方下一步的倾向", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 515073}, {"id": 230404, "content": "真的生气了么，真的伤心了么", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 319918}, {"id": 230916, "content": "天下雨", "image": "img/option/option/20170822120134snfjOKIUkFlQH9EC.jpg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1101929}, {"id": 229893, "content": "观察力敏感到能很快发现店员笨不笨尊不尊重说没说谎，然后敏感到观察出这些就心生离意", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950981}, {"id": 230405, "content": "是不是处", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1108706}, {"id": 229894, "content": "看标题猜出是不是软文", "image": null, "praise_count": 159, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 33379}, {"id": 230406, "content": "预知未来", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1108724}, {"id": 229895, "content": "轻松发现所有人的喜好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107084}, {"id": 229896, "content": "做愛", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 977380}, {"id": 230152, "content": "做爱吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107703}, {"id": 229897, "content": "男性的的长处是不是真的长", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 879685}, {"id": 230921, "content": "选择东西时别人是不是其实不喜欢", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1111150}, {"id": 301833, "content": "别人的习惯，细节", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1458837}, {"id": 229898, "content": "他不爱我", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1079360}, {"id": 230154, "content": "从对方的一言一行和对对方的第一印象用直觉就能判断对方的人品或是性格，适不适合做朋友或者处事，八九不离十。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 430884}, {"id": 229899, "content": "辨识美女方面特准", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1104368}, {"id": 339212, "content": "空间里凭留言判断出他和她或者他和她的关系哈哈哈。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1637585}, {"id": 229900, "content": "淘宝搜索页面一目十行。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1094092}, {"id": 230156, "content": "这个男人到底爱不爱这个女人", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107717}, {"id": 250636, "content": "穿着品牌", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1190637}, {"id": 229901, "content": "鉴螺达人", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 871628}, {"id": 230157, "content": "看价格和封面就知道是不是正品", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1099319}, {"id": 258573, "content": "同事：“这是什么？”\n我：“尝尝看....”", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1233681}, {"id": 230158, "content": "是不是假发", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1085541}, {"id": 260878, "content": "什么都不懂  也什么都看不出来……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1244079}, {"id": 262415, "content": "跟我能不能合得来", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1249355}, {"id": 229903, "content": "身边的人是不是在说谎，哪怕是善意的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1098794}, {"id": 230159, "content": "帮老师批作业，检查错别字，以及别人的情绪，在我眼里通通一览无余", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1069618}, {"id": 229904, "content": "哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1}, {"id": 230160, "content": "虫子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 618373}, {"id": 230928, "content": "嗅到奸情的味道", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1111189}, {"id": 229905, "content": "哈哈哈哈哈\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1}, {"id": 230161, "content": "观察是否大姨妈期间", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1084360}, {"id": 229906, "content": "跟人说话时会注意对方的面部表情，猜测对方对我说的内容的真实想法。以及对方说话之前可能有些哪些心理活动。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1050274}, {"id": 230162, "content": "是不是渣男\n是不是能获奥斯卡奖的电影\n是不是能大火的书\n是不是能成为cp", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 468602}, {"id": 229907, "content": "别人的借口总是第一时间看穿，但看破不说破是水瓶座最后的温柔", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 416515}, {"id": 230163, "content": "能观察到很多细节？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 